🆕From fork() to Fleet: Designing an Agent Sandbox Cloud

https://t.co/qA8g9FtJeS

@abshkbh spoke at AIEWF Online last year about Arrakis, his open source MicroVM-based secure sandboxes. @gdb hired him immediately for his expertise and passion - and now, after a year at OpenAI and recent release of @ChatGPTApp Work, he makes his onstage debut covering the three pillars of agent cloud engineering - Runtime, Persistence, and Orchestration - and ends with a surprising conclusion on why storage and filesystems are an integral part of agent clouds!
